    "title": "Why Agentic AI Is Security's Next Blind Spot",
    "description": "Agentic AI is already running in production environments across many organizations today. It is executing tasks, consuming data, and taking actions — most likely without meaningful involvement from the security team. The industry conversation has largely framed this as a question of policy: allow it, restrict it, or monitor it? However, that framing misses the point.&nbsp;\nThe more urgent",
